description:
This package contains all the binaries for the Windows API Code Pack needed for Windows Forms Development in the 1.1 version, released by Microsoft in 2009.
		 

			Modifications by Jacob Slusser until 2020. Modified to use .NET Frameworks 4.6.2 - 4.8.1 or .NET 6, 8 & 9 and refactoring by Peter William Wagner, (aka Wagnerp) 2023 - 2024.
title: WindowsAPICodePack
